sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Box, Typography, Paper, Grid, TextField, FormControl, FormLabel, FormGroup, FormControlLabel, Checkbox, MenuItem, Select, InputLabel, InputAdornment } from '@mui/material'; const Zoning = ({ formik }) => { return ( Zoning Information Enter zoning and land use information for the property. {/* Basic Zoning Information */} Zoning Classification Current Use {/* Land Metrics */} Land Metrics { formik.handleChange(e); // Update acres when square feet change if (e.target.value) { formik.setFieldValue('landArea', (parseFloat(e.target.value) / 43560).toFixed(4)); } }} /> %, inputProps: { min: 0, max: 100 } }} value={formik.values.maxBuildingCoverage || ''} onChange={formik.handleChange} /> {/* Setbacks */} Required Setbacks {/* Parking Requirements */} Parking Requirements {/* Zoning Restrictions */} Zoning Restrictions & Compliance Zoning Status } label="Conforming Use" /> } label="Legal Non-Conforming Use" /> } label="Zoning Variance Granted" /> } label="Special Use Permit" /> Future Development } label="Rezoning Potential" /> } label="Expansion Potential" /> } label="Potential for More Dense Use" /> } label="In Opportunity Zone" /> {/* Additional Notes */} ); }; export default Zoning;
